 Park, Kuala Lumpur.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_separator][vc_column_text]If you&#8217;re interested, send in your resume to <a href=\"mailto:stella@durianbb.com\">stella@durianbb.com<\/a> with the headline &#8212; &#8220;<strong>Resume Submission for Customer Service Representative<\/strong>&#8220;.[\/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=&#8221;41&#8243; img_size=&#8221;large&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]DurianBB is looking for a Customer Service rockstar who is passionate about delivering happiness! As we expand our businesses in major Asian cities, we are looking to work with an experienced personnel who is interested to learn about ecommerce and all the key elements that goes into the making of DurianBB brand. Join our team &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/durianbb.com.my\/wanted-customer-service-representative\/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Wanted: Customer Service Representative<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":77,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"image","meta":{"jetpack_post_was_ever_published":false,"_jetpack_newsletter_access":"","_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs":false,"_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id":0,"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content":false,"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":"","jetpack_publicize_message":"","jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled":true,"jetpack_social_post_already_shared":true,"jetpack_social_options":{"image_generator_settings":{"template":"highway","enabled":false},"version":2}},"categories":[50518641],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5317","post","type-post","status-publish","format-image","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-career","post_format-post-format-image"],"jetpack_publicize_connections":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/